						<p><div class="item">
<h2><a class="listing" style="link" href="/en/Dossiers/CTA-and-S-T/S-T-organisations/International/European-South-Africa-Science-and-Technology-Advancement-Programme-ESASTAP" title="European-South Africa Science and Technology Advancement Programme (ESASTAP) " alt="link">European-South Africa Science and Technology Advancement Programme (ESASTAP) </a></h2>

	
					<p>This programme, implemented by the South African Department of Science and Technology (DST) and funded by the European Commission under the Sixth Framework Programme (FP6), will significantly enhance the support and assistance available to both South African and European researchers to leverage mutual benefits from this partnership. Through enhanced networking and partnering, scientists and institutions from the EU and South Africa can jointly explore new and emerging scientific and technological areas, anticipate future science and technology needs, and cooperatively seek to resolve major global issues. </p>
							<p><span class="date">27/10/2006</span></p>
	<div class="cnt">
	<a class="link" href="/en/Dossiers/CTA-and-S-T/S-T-organisations/International/European-South-Africa-Science-and-Technology-Advancement-Programme-ESASTAP">Read more...</a>
</div>
<br class="cl">
