<h2><a class="listing" style="link" href="/en/Dossiers/CTA-and-S-T/S-T-organisations/International/EU-Water-Initiative-EUWI-ERA-Net" title="EU Water Initiative, EUWI-ERA-Net" alt="link">EU Water Initiative, EUWI-ERA-Net</a></h2>

	
					<p>As the research component of the <b>EU Water Initiative</b>, EUWI-era.net is an initiative (under FP6) to establish a framework for long-term communication, collaboration and coordination of member state research programmes related to water issues in developing countries. The scheme will also enable national systems to take on tasks collectively that they would not have been able to tackle independently.<a href="http://www.euwi-era.net/index.php?id=1" target="_self">http://www.euwi-era.net/index.php?id=1</a>&nbsp;For information on the research component of the EU Water Initiative, visit<a href="http://europa.eu.int/comm/research/water-initiative/index_en.html" target="_self">http://europa.eu.int/comm/research/water-initiative/index_en.html</a>and <a href="http://cordis.europa.eu/coordination/era-net.htm" target="_self">http://cordis.europa.eu/coordination/era-net.htm</a> </p>
