						<p><div class="item">
<h2><a class="listing" style="link" href="/en/Dossiers/CTA-and-S-T/S-T-organisations/International/EDULINK-ACP-EU-Cooperation-Programme-in-Higher-Education" title="EDULINK: ACP-EU Cooperation Programme in Higher Education" alt="link">EDULINK: ACP-EU Cooperation Programme in Higher Education</a></h2>

	
					<p>EDULINK aims to foster capacity building and regional integration in the field of higher education through institutional networking, and to support a quality higher education system that is relevant to the needs of the labour market and consistent with ACP socio-economic development priorities. EDULINK is open to all ACP countries and to the 15 EU Member States that are signatories to the 9th European Development Fund (EDF). Joint projects submitted by networks of ACP and European Higher Education Institutions (HEIs) will be identified through open calls for proposals. EDULINK promotes networking of HEIs in ACP States and the eligible EU Member States through funding of joint projects. As such, it does not provide funding for individuals and is not a scolarship programme.</p>
							<p><span class="date">24/08/2007</span></p>
	<div class="cnt">
	<a class="link" href="/en/Dossiers/CTA-and-S-T/S-T-organisations/International/EDULINK-ACP-EU-Cooperation-Programme-in-Higher-Education">Read more...</a>
